    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 0, $$What is that?! What is that doof-doof-doof noise? A cat? A mouse? A visitor in the house?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "What is that?! What is that doof-doof-doof noise?", "bbox": [692.6, 58.1, 1008.2, 104.8], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "A cat? A mouse? A visitor in the house?", "bbox": [759.6, 136.2, 941.2, 208.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 1, $$No, it’s something even furrier than a cat, even cuter than a mouse, and much tinier than you and me.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "No, it’s something even furrier than a cat, even cuter than a mouse, and much tinier than you and me.", "bbox": [112.3, 84.2, 454.6, 156.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 2, $$It’s the three Doof-Doofs. These sweet creatures have only one foot each to hop on. And each hop makes a thumping doof-doof on the floor.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "It’s the three Doof-Doofs.", "bbox": [746.8, 58.1, 954.0, 78.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "These sweet creatures have only one foot each to hop on. And each hop makes a thumping doof-doof on the floor.", "bbox": [676.6, 110.2, 1024.2, 182.8], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 3, $$ahhhh uhh who is Here always is Solly thinking Doof, looooong the smart and one, loud. He uhhs and ahhs and doof-doofs all night long.$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "ahhhh uhh", "bbox": [369.0, 46.5, 524.8, 172.7], "size": 52.5}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "who is Here always is Solly thinking Doof, looooong the smart and one, loud.", "bbox": [672.4, 110.2, 1028.3, 156.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He uhhs and ahhs and doof-doofs all night long.", "bbox": [630.6, 184.8, 1070.2, 208.8], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 4, $$He reads daytime stories to the other Doof-Doofs, because unlike you and me, that is when they sleep. Thinky, stinky Solly Doof prefers reading over bathing any time.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "He reads daytime stories to the other Doof-Doofs, because unlike you and me, that is when they sleep.", "bbox": [634.4, 110.2, 1066.4, 156.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Thinky, stinky Solly Doof prefers reading over bathing any time.", "bbox": [683.2, 188.2, 1017.6, 234.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 5, $$And here is Sally Doof, the smallest and sweetest Doof-Doof of the three. In a little quiet voice she sings doobee-doobee Doof-Doof songs, when it gets a bit too quiet in the night.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "And here is Sally Doof, the smallest and sweetest Doof-Doof of the three.", "bbox": [77.8, 58.1, 489.2, 104.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "In a little quiet voice she sings doobee-doobee Doof-Doof songs, when it gets a bit too quiet in the night.", "bbox": [120.8, 136.2, 446.2, 208.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 6, $$She likes finding shiny things and cuddles. Snuggly, huggly Sally Doof who loves to sing. clink clankclunk$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "She likes finding shiny things and cuddles. Snuggly, huggly Sally Doof who loves to sing.", "bbox": [68.9, 91.7, 441.4, 137.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "clink clankclunk", "bbox": [347.5, 213.3, 707.6, 330.2], "size": 53.1}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 7, $$Don’t forget Silly Doof, the funniest Doof-Doof in the house. He is always joking. hahahahaha! Wiggly, giggly Silly Doof will make you laugh until your tummy hurts. He cheers up the other Doof-Doofs whenever they feel sad.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Don’t forget Silly Doof, the funniest Doof-Doof in the house. He is always joking.", "bbox": [93.5, 58.1, 473.4, 104.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "hahahahaha!", "bbox": [106.4, 198.9, 392.0, 334.3], "size": 54.9}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Wiggly, giggly Silly Doof will make you laugh until your tummy hurts.", "bbox": [658.8, 58.1, 1025.0, 104.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He cheers up the other Doof-Doofs whenever they feel sad.", "bbox": [698.5, 136.2, 985.3, 182.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 8, $$He loves to dance on his big silly foot, to the songs that Sally Doof sings.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "He loves to dance on his big silly foot, to the songs that Sally Doof sings.", "bbox": [127.8, 84.2, 439.1, 130.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 9, $$So, if at night you ever hear a strange doof-doof noise again, remember, it’s just the three Doof-Doofs, reading, singing and dancing on their one doof-doof foot.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "So, if at night you ever hear a strange doof-doof noise again, remember, it’s just the three Doof-Doofs, reading, singing and dancing on their one doof-doof foot.", "bbox": [681.7, 84.2, 1019.1, 208.8], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 10, $$So sleep well, little one. Or keep one eye open...$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "So sleep well, little one. Or keep one eye open...", "bbox": [752.0, 84.2, 948.8, 130.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 11, $$Because maybe, just maybe, you’ll see three cute little creatures hopping past on one foot, going doof-doof-doof.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Because maybe, just maybe, you’ll see three cute little creatures hopping past on one foot, going doof-doof-doof.", "bbox": [704.3, 58.1, 996.5, 156.8], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('the-three-doof-doofs', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 0, $$There was once a very old and very tired lioness. She was so tired that she slept all day. And all night.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "There was once a very old and very tired lioness.", "bbox": [107.0, 170.2, 393.5, 224.7], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She was so tired that she slept all day. And all night.", "bbox": [236.2, 331.2, 461.4, 417.1], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 1, $$“Come and hunt with us,” said her sisters and daughters. But the lioness was too tired.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Come and hunt with us,” said her sisters and daughters.", "bbox": [664.0, 186.2, 988.3, 240.7], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "But the lioness was too tired.", "bbox": [824.9, 364.5, 1032.7, 420.0], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 2, $$“What’s wrong with her?” asked the young impalas. “Don’t go too close,” warned their mothers. “She might eat you.” But the lioness just flicked her ears to chase away the flies.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“What’s wrong with her?” asked the young impalas. “Don’t go too close,” warned their mothers. “She might eat you.”", "bbox": [102.9, 145.5, 470.8, 260.5], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "But the lioness just flicked her ears to chase away the flies.", "bbox": [240.9, 348.0, 468.4, 433.6], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 3, $$One day the lioness woke up with a strange feeling that something was watching her. When she looked up she saw a boiling roiling creature in the tree. “Who are you?” asked the lioness.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "One day the lioness woke up with a strange feeling that something was watching her.", "bbox": [660.5, 137.7, 980.9, 223.2], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "When she looked up she saw a boiling roiling creature in the tree.", "bbox": [660.5, 316.9, 1022.1, 371.9], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Who are you?” asked the lioness.", "bbox": [660.5, 399.6, 1028.5, 425.1], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 4, $$“I am the sun. I have come to fetch you.” “Go away,” grumbled the lioness. “I want to sleep.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I am the sun. I have come to fetch you.”", "bbox": [102.2, 173.7, 387.3, 229.2], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Go away,” grumbled the lioness. “I want to sleep.”", "bbox": [234.7, 331.9, 464.0, 416.9], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 5, $$When the lioness opened her eyes again, the sun was still in the tree. “Can’t you see, you are making us all hot and thirsty?” “It’s getting late,” said the sun. “Follow me.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When the lioness opened her eyes again, the sun was still in the tree. “Can’t you see, you are making us all hot and thirsty?”", "bbox": [672.8, 141.4, 1046.1, 256.9], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“It’s getting late,” said the sun. “Follow me.”", "bbox": [672.8, 365.6, 858.5, 450.6], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 6, $$So the lioness slowly got up and followed the sun. “Happy hunting,” called her sisters and daughters after her. “See you! See you!” chirped the bird.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "So the lioness slowly got up and followed the sun.", "bbox": [98.7, 166.6, 413.6, 222.1], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Happy hunting,” called her sisters and daughters after her. “See you! See you!” chirped the bird.", "bbox": [90.7, 333.9, 493.7, 433.6], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 7, $$But the lioness didn’t hear anything. She just climbed higher and higher and higher into the sky.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "But the lioness didn’t hear anything.", "bbox": [665.0, 173.8, 891.7, 229.3], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She just climbed higher and higher and higher into the sky.", "bbox": [765.1, 328.7, 1015.0, 414.2], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 8, $$“Phew, it is far,” said the lioness.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Phew, it is far,” said the lioness.", "bbox": [272.1, 111.4, 443.7, 165.8], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 9, $$“Not too far to go anymore,” said the sun. “You can rest when we get there.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Not too far to go anymore,” said the sun. “You can rest when we get there.”", "bbox": [667.6, 387.8, 1038.2, 472.8], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 10, $$And so the lioness came to stay with the sun. All day she lay lazily in its warmth.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "And so the lioness came to stay with the sun. All day she lay lazily in its warmth.", "bbox": [107.7, 94.5, 368.6, 210.0], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 11, $$But at night, when the sun was asleep, she looked down at the beautiful world she had left behind.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "But at night, when the sun was asleep, she looked down at the beautiful world she had left behind.", "bbox": [704.4, 362.7, 1021.5, 478.2], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('the-very-tired-lioness', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 0, $$Every December Gugu and Cici travel with Mom to Joburg. Their best bit? Riding the long-distance train together.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Every December Gugu and Cici travel with Mom to Joburg.", "bbox": [648.1, 387.1, 950.2, 437.1], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Their best bit? Riding the long-distance train together.", "bbox": [661.0, 456.4, 937.3, 506.4], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 1, $$“This year I’m taking the window seat!” says Cici. “Not fair! You had it last year,” Gugu shouts.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“This year I’m taking the window seat!” says Cici.", "bbox": [153.0, 126.4, 387.0, 176.4], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Not fair! You had it last year,” Gugu shouts.", "bbox": [126.1, 195.7, 413.9, 245.7], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 2, $$“Race!” says Gugu. Off they go, running down the platform. Cici reaches it first.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Race!” says Gugu.", "bbox": [193.8, 134.2, 373.1, 155.2], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Off they go, running down the platform.", "bbox": [185.9, 174.5, 381.0, 224.5], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Cici reaches it first.", "bbox": [193.2, 243.9, 373.7, 264.9], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 3, $$“Rock, paper, scissors!” says Cici. This time, Gugu wins.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Rock, paper, scissors!” says Cici.", "bbox": [657.9, 397.7, 878.5, 447.7], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "This time, Gugu wins.", "bbox": [667.9, 467.0, 868.5, 488.0], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 4, $$Mom decides, “You’ll share the window. Half the trip is for Gugu, half for Cici.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Mom decides, “You’ll share the window. Half the trip is for Gugu, half for Cici.”", "bbox": [693.5, 405.7, 1007.3, 484.7], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 5, $$They get on the train. No! Every window seat is taken.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "They get on the train.", "bbox": [755.6, 368.4, 963.2, 389.4], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "No! Every window seat is taken.", "bbox": [747.0, 408.8, 966.1, 458.8], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 6, $$The sisters sit in the aisle seats. They peek at the window. They wish they could see the view.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The sisters sit in the aisle seats. They peek at the window. They wish they could see the view.", "bbox": [711.8, 243.6, 1013.1, 322.6], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 7, $$The lady sitting in the window seat drops her handbag. The sisters pick it up and hand it back.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The lady sitting in the window seat drops her handbag.", "bbox": [90.2, 279.6, 424.3, 329.6], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The sisters pick it up and hand it back.", "bbox": [137.5, 348.9, 377.0, 398.9], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 8, $$“Thank you, girls. Would you like to sit here by the window?” “Yes!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Thank you, girls. Would you like to sit here by the window?” “Yes!”", "bbox": [715.1, 337.7, 990.0, 465.7], "size": 27.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 9, $$Gugu leans close to the window. “Into the tunnel!” she yells.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Gugu leans close to the window. “Into the tunnel!” she yells.", "bbox": [666.0, 245.6, 779.4, 411.6], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 10, $$Out comes the sun again. Cici jumps into the window seat. “Look!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Out comes the sun again.", "bbox": [741.4, 172.8, 987.7, 193.8], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Cici jumps into the window seat. “Look!”", "bbox": [775.8, 291.2, 953.3, 390.2], "size": 27.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 11, $$Finally they fall asleep. They will wake up in Joburg. They can’t wait to tell Tata what they saw.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Finally they fall asleep. They will wake up in Joburg.", "bbox": [740.2, 194.8, 960.6, 273.8], "size": 21.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "They can’t wait to tell Tata what they saw.", "bbox": [747.0, 293.1, 953.8, 343.1], "size": 21.0}]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('the-window-seat', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 0, $$My friends and I have a game we like to play. “There’s a fire on the mountain. Run, run! Kukh’umlilo kwezontaba. Baleka, baleka!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "My friends and I have a game we like to play.", "bbox": [849.4, 334.0, 988.9, 398.6], "size": 19.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“There’s a fire on the mountain. Run, run! Kukh’umlilo kwezontaba. Baleka, baleka!”", "bbox": [628.1, 436.7, 922.0, 501.3], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 1, $$Then one day there was a real fire on the mountain. It was a terrible fire that burned and burned.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Then one day there was a real fire on the mountain. It was a terrible fire that burned and burned.", "bbox": [684.8, 455.9, 1016.0, 520.5], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 2, $$Big, old buildings burned, books burned, trees and grasses burned. Helicopters tipped water onto the fire and brave firefighters blasted their hoses.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Big, old buildings burned, books burned, trees and grasses burned. Helicopters tipped water onto the fire and brave firefighters blasted their hoses.", "bbox": [139.8, 342.5, 417.3, 475.5], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 3, $$And people did run. They grabbed their books and bags and ran away from the smoke and the flames.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "And people did run. They grabbed their books and bags and ran away from the smoke and the flames.", "bbox": [79.0, 360.2, 475.1, 424.8], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 4, $$After three long days, the last flames were out. The firefighters could finally rest.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "After three long days, the last flames were out.", "bbox": [734.4, 89.5, 952.2, 131.3], "size": 19.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The firefighters could finally rest.", "bbox": [703.1, 157.9, 983.5, 176.9], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 5, $$The slopes of the mountain were black. When we walked on the mountain, all we could see were rocks and burnt bushes. We were very sad.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The slopes of the mountain were black. When we walked on the mountain, all we could see were rocks and burnt bushes.", "bbox": [641.3, 90.9, 1062.3, 155.5], "size": 19.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "We were very sad.", "bbox": [774.3, 182.1, 929.3, 201.1], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 6, $$Until one day … tiny bits of red popped up through the black. “Look, look. What is that?”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Until one day … tiny bits of red popped up through the black.", "bbox": [720.1, 180.2, 980.7, 222.0], "size": 19.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Look, look. What is that?”", "bbox": [740.8, 248.6, 960.0, 267.6], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 7, $$The little bits of red grew and grew until they became beautiful fire lilies, tall and elegant with drooping red bells for flowers.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The little bits of red grew and grew until they became beautiful fire lilies, tall and elegant with drooping red bells for flowers.", "bbox": [650.3, 89.6, 901.7, 276.7], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 8, $$Then came the big, red flowers bursting through the green like volcanoes. They looked like thick red tubes with yellow- topped spikes and big, red petals. Dots of green grew up all over the mountainside, turning the black into green grasses and restios.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Then came the big, red flowers bursting through the green like volcanoes. They looked like thick red tubes with yellow- topped spikes and big, red petals.", "bbox": [693.8, 72.5, 1036.7, 159.9], "size": 19.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Dots of green grew up all over the mountainside, turning the black into green grasses and restios.", "bbox": [729.8, 186.5, 1029.5, 251.1], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 9, $$asparagusfernsunfolding in wetpatchesaftertheran i were . here t nehT And the tall in watsonia orange and pink.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "asparagusfernsunfolding in wetpatchesaftertheran i were . here t nehT", "bbox": [109.3, 59.0, 461.8, 352.6], "size": 11.9}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "And the tall in watsonia orange and pink.", "bbox": [941.8, 238.3, 1039.6, 325.7], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 10, $$Soon the mountainside was covered with plants we hadn’t seen for years.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Soon the mountainside was covered with plants we hadn’t seen for years.", "bbox": [638.7, 85.2, 893.4, 149.8], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 11, $$The mountain is full of new life!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The mountain is full of new life!", "bbox": [711.5, 78.2, 977.9, 97.2], "size": 19.0}]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('theres-a-fire-on-the-mountain', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 0, $$There’s an alien in my house... We are under attack!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "There’s an alien in my house... We are under attack!", "bbox": [142.8, 249.9, 424.1, 305.9], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 1, $$The walls are changing colour. It must be the alien. The air is getting warmer. It must be the alien.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The walls are changing colour. It must be the alien. The air is getting warmer. It must be the alien.", "bbox": [140.9, 223.2, 425.8, 351.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 2, $$Strangers keep coming. It must be the alien.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Strangers keep coming. It must be the alien.", "bbox": [171.7, 256.3, 395.2, 312.3], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 3, $$We need protection. I build a fort. Mom and Dad normally build with me, but these days I feel invisible. It must be the alien.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "We need protection. I build a fort.", "bbox": [873.1, 292.1, 1063.1, 348.1], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Mom and Dad normally build with me, but these days I feel invisible. It must be the alien.", "bbox": [722.1, 395.8, 1080.8, 487.8], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 4, $$Iheara weird noise in the middleofthenight. It mustbethealien.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Iheara weird noise in the middleofthenight.", "bbox": [134.3, 138.5, 529.0, 268.8], "size": 22.1}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "It mustbethealien.", "bbox": [725.5, 136.1, 894.4, 240.7], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 5, $$We are under attack! I am an army of one.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "We are under attack! I am an army of one.", "bbox": [743.6, 249.2, 943.0, 305.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 6, $$1 step, 2 step... I am the army. 3 step, 4 step... Ready for battle.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "1 step, 2 step... I am the army.", "bbox": [209.3, 59.3, 363.4, 115.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "3 step, 4 step... Ready for battle.", "bbox": [794.9, 59.3, 965.8, 115.3], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 7, $$5 step, 6 step... Away with you, alien!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "5 step, 6 step... Away with you, alien!", "bbox": [767.1, 130.2, 979.0, 186.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 8, $$7 step, 8 step... I get closer.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "7 step, 8 step... I get closer.", "bbox": [207.1, 67.1, 345.7, 123.1], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 9, $$9 step, 10 step... I am by its head. Woah! I get a fright. It is tiny and it... ...looks like me?! How can that be? Is it really an alien?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "9 step, 10 step... I am by its head.", "bbox": [205.4, 174.1, 361.5, 230.1], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Woah! I get a fright. It is tiny and it...", "bbox": [190.0, 282.1, 377.0, 338.1], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "...looks like me?! How can that be? Is it really an alien?", "bbox": [761.7, 72.7, 943.2, 164.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 10, $$Maybe it’s a friend. Maybe it’s my friend?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Maybe it’s a friend. Maybe it’s my friend?", "bbox": [749.0, 59.9, 952.0, 115.9], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 11, $$1 step, 2 step... We are now an army of two.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "1 step, 2 step... We are now an army of two.", "bbox": [154.2, 258.4, 422.7, 314.4], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('theres-an-alien-in-my-house', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 0, $$Thuli stays with her grandmother and their cow, Special, in the village. Her parents work in the city.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Thuli stays with her grandmother and their cow, Special, in the village.", "bbox": [132.0, 101.2, 434.9, 145.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Her parents work in the city.", "bbox": [168.2, 173.2, 398.7, 193.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 1, $$Every morning her grandmother wakes Thuli up early to go to watch the sunrise. When the sun is up in the sky, Grandmother bathes Thuli. She brushes Thuli’s teeth, washes her face, and brushes her hair.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Every morning her grandmother wakes Thuli up early to go to watch the sunrise.", "bbox": [118.3, 220.7, 448.6, 264.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "When the sun is up in the sky, Grandmother bathes Thuli. She brushes Thuli’s teeth, washes her face, and brushes her hair.", "bbox": [115.0, 292.7, 451.9, 384.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 2, $$When Thuli is nice and clean, Grandmother gives Thuli some porridge. Thuli loves the porridge. But she loves the milk more, because it comes from their cow, Special. The milk is fresh and creamy.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When Thuli is nice and clean, Grandmother gives Thuli some porridge. Thuli loves the porridge. But she loves the milk more, because it comes from their cow, Special.", "bbox": [682.1, 333.6, 1018.7, 449.6], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The milk is fresh and creamy.", "bbox": [732.2, 477.6, 968.6, 497.6], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 3, $$After eating, Thuli and Grandmother sit under the tree, and Grandmother tells Thuli stories.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "After eating, Thuli and Grandmother sit under the tree, and Grandmother tells Thuli stories.", "bbox": [690.9, 268.7, 1009.9, 336.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 4, $$When the stories are finished, Grandmother gives Thuli some cookies and a glass of milk, fresh and creamy. Thuli’s parents bring the cookies with them when they visit. Chocolate chip cookies. Thuli’s favourite.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When the stories are finished, Grandmother gives Thuli some cookies and a glass of milk, fresh and creamy.", "bbox": [127.0, 220.7, 439.9, 288.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Thuli’s parents bring the cookies with them when they visit. Chocolate chip cookies. Thuli’s favourite.", "bbox": [132.5, 316.7, 434.5, 384.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 5, $$Special always looks at Thuli as she eats her cookies. Thuli wants to share her cookies with Special, but Grandmother gives her only enough for herself.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Special always looks at Thuli as she eats her cookies. Thuli wants to share her cookies with Special, but Grandmother gives her only enough for herself.", "bbox": [110.0, 77.2, 428.5, 169.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 6, $$That day, after listening to the stories, Thuli follows Grandmother into the house, tiptoeing so that Grandmother doesn’t hear. Thuli sees Grandmother take the cookies out of a cake tin inside the oven.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "That day, after listening to the stories, Thuli follows Grandmother into the house, tiptoeing so that Grandmother doesn’t hear.", "bbox": [132.4, 220.7, 434.6, 312.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Thuli sees Grandmother take the cookies out of a cake tin inside the oven.", "bbox": [120.1, 340.7, 446.9, 384.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 7, $$Thuli runs back outside and tells Special that soon she will share her cookies with her.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Thuli runs back outside and tells Special that soon she will share her cookies with her.", "bbox": [143.0, 268.7, 423.9, 336.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 8, $$Later in the afternoon, Grandmother and Thuli take a nap, then wake up to watch the sunset.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Later in the afternoon, Grandmother and Thuli take a nap, then wake up to watch the sunset.", "bbox": [686.1, 268.7, 1014.8, 336.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 9, $$When the sun sets, Thuli sneaks off into the kitchen.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When the sun sets, Thuli sneaks off into the kitchen.", "bbox": [690.5, 280.7, 1010.3, 324.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 10, $$She opens the oven, and takes out cookies for Special.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "She opens the oven, and takes out cookies for Special.", "bbox": [116.2, 280.7, 450.8, 324.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('thuli-special-and-the-secret', 11, $$Special licks Thuli when she gives her the cookies. Special smiles. Thuli smiles. “It’s our little secret,” she says.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Special licks Thuli when she gives her the cookies.", "bbox": [117.2, 214.5, 449.8, 258.5], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Special smiles. Thuli smiles.", "bbox": [173.3, 286.5, 393.6, 306.5], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“It’s our little secret,” she says.", "bbox": [146.1, 343.6, 420.8, 390.9], "size": 26.5}]$$),
