    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 0, $$Yapo loves to play with his soccer ball! He often tries dribbling tricks with his dad. An elastico, a rainbow flick and even...$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Yapo loves to play with his soccer ball!", "bbox": [644.9, 168.4, 998.7, 186.4], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He often tries dribbling tricks with his dad. An elastico, a rainbow flick and even...", "bbox": [644.9, 220.4, 1033.9, 264.4], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 1, $$... a bicycle kick!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "... a bicycle kick!", "bbox": [155.9, 108.8, 302.9, 126.8], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 2, $$Yapo is the star of the Under 6 Team of Tino Football Club. He is quick and nimble on the field. Yapo scores most of the goals for his team.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Yapo is the star of the Under 6 Team of Tino Football Club. He is quick and nimble on the field. Yapo scores most of the goals for his team.", "bbox": [78.0, 136.3, 445.2, 232.3], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 3, $$Yapo, however, does not like to pass the ball. Coach Tazi often reminds Yapo to share the ball with his teammates.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Yapo, however, does not like to pass the ball. Coach Tazi often reminds Yapo to share the ball with his teammates.", "bbox": [78.0, 200.8, 401.7, 296.8], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 4, $$One day, Tino Football Club was playing Kuma Football Club. Yapo tried many times to score but the Kuma team was too strong. By half-time, Kuma was leading 2 – 0.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "One day, Tino Football Club was playing Kuma Football Club. Yapo tried many times to score but the Kuma team was too strong.", "bbox": [78.0, 95.9, 473.7, 165.9], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "By half-time, Kuma was leading 2 – 0.", "bbox": [78.0, 199.9, 422.5, 217.9], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "TINO", "bbox": [717.2, 110.9, 789.2, 140.9], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "KUMA", "bbox": [919.8, 107.4, 1009.2, 137.4], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 5, $$Coach Tazi gave the team a stern pep talk, ‘Play together and pass the ball to whoever is free! Yapo, pass the ball!’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Coach Tazi gave the team a stern pep talk, ‘Play together and pass the ball to whoever is free!", "bbox": [78.0, 108.7, 404.8, 178.7], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Yapo, pass the ball!’", "bbox": [78.0, 212.7, 257.8, 230.7], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 6, $$When Yapo was the made second to half sit on began, the bench. His teammates were a little scared to play without him, but they remembered to play together. Nat scored the first goal for the Tino team. ‘WOOHOO!’ cheered the crowd. Three minutes before the end of the game, Lindi scored the team’s second goal! ‘LADUMA!’ they shouted.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When Yapo was the made second to half sit on began, the bench. His teammates were a little scared to play without him, but they remembered to play together.", "bbox": [78.0, 61.2, 400.2, 183.2], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Nat scored the first goal for the Tino team.", "bbox": [78.0, 217.2, 296.8, 261.2], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "TINO", "bbox": [362.3, 280.0, 398.7, 297.4], "size": 15.8}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "KUMA", "bbox": [452.3, 287.2, 497.6, 304.5], "size": 15.8}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘WOOHOO!’ cheered the crowd.", "bbox": [637.8, 65.7, 1036.6, 101.7], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Three minutes before the end of the game, Lindi scored the team’s second goal!", "bbox": [637.8, 124.7, 1023.0, 168.7], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘LADUMA!’ they shouted.", "bbox": [637.8, 201.7, 832.5, 258.7], "size": 27.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 7, $$Coach Tazi called Yapo back into the game, ‘The score is now 2 – 2. Take us home, boy! Remember to play with your teammates!’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Coach Tazi called Yapo back into the game, ‘The score is now 2 – 2. Take us home, boy!", "bbox": [78.0, 96.2, 469.1, 140.2], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Remember to play with your teammates!’", "bbox": [78.0, 174.2, 455.6, 192.2], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "TINO", "bbox": [650.6, 124.7, 689.0, 150.2], "size": 19.4}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "KUMA", "bbox": [750.1, 96.8, 797.5, 124.5], "size": 20.1}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 8, $$Lindi kicked the ball to Nat, who passed it to Yapo. Yapo dribbled between two opponents and when he was about to take a shot, he spotted another Kuma player running towards him. Yapo saw Lindi following close behind, remembered Coach Tazi and passed the ball to her. Lindi turned towards the goal, and took her best shot!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Lindi kicked the ball to Nat, who passed it to Yapo.", "bbox": [56.7, 61.2, 307.0, 105.2], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Yapo dribbled between two opponents and when he was about to take a shot, he spotted another Kuma player running towards him.", "bbox": [114.8, 172.4, 434.1, 268.4], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Yapo saw Lindi following close behind, remembered Coach Tazi and passed the ball to her.", "bbox": [56.7, 335.8, 299.6, 431.8], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Lindi turned towards the goal, and took her best shot!", "bbox": [293.1, 436.9, 489.5, 506.9], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 9, $$‘GOAL!’ cried Coach Tazi. The Tino crowd went wild with joy as Lindi’s teammates ran to hug her! Yapo was very happy that his team had won 3 – 2. But he was a little disappointed that he had not scored any goals.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘GOAL!’ cried Coach Tazi.", "bbox": [173.4, 50.5, 401.6, 140.6], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The Tino crowd went wild with joy as Lindi’s teammates ran to hug her!", "bbox": [248.7, 174.6, 488.6, 244.6], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "TINO", "bbox": [816.3, 170.6, 854.3, 192.1], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "DECOR", "text": "KUMA", "bbox": [924.0, 152.0, 971.4, 175.7], "size": 18.6}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Yapo was very happy that his team had won 3 – 2. But he was a little disappointed that he had not scored any goals.", "bbox": [773.9, 408.4, 1066.2, 504.4], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 10, $$‘Congratulations for a mighty comeback!’ beamed Coach Tazi to his team. ‘Well done, Yapo, for passing the ball to Lindi.’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Congratulations for a mighty comeback!’ beamed Coach Tazi to his team.", "bbox": [637.8, 157.6, 1014.1, 201.6], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Well done, Yapo, for passing the ball to Lindi.’", "bbox": [637.8, 235.6, 1057.5, 253.6], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 11, $$‘You may not have scored a goal today, but you certainly helped your team to win. Well done, son!’ smiled Dad, as they walked home together.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘You may not have scored a goal today, but you certainly helped your team to win. Well done, son!’ smiled Dad, as they walked home together.", "bbox": [78.0, 163.2, 473.7, 259.2], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('yapo-saves-the-day', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 0, $$“What do you want to be when you grow up?” asks Teacher Langa.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“What do you want to be when you grow up?” asks Teacher Langa.", "bbox": [658.7, 97.5, 902.9, 181.4], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 1, $$Story spread 2 Khutso shouts, “I want to be a cook!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Story spread 2", "bbox": [-142.4, -122.0, 27.8, -98.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "Khutso shouts, “I want to be a cook!”", "bbox": [56.7, 448.9, 480.1, 519.2], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 2, $$I love helping my mom bake and cook at home.” Nandi says, “No! That’s a girl’s job. My mom does all the cooking at home.” “Yes he can, Nandi. You can be anything you want to be,” says Teacher Langa. The class chants, “Yes you can!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "I love helping my mom bake and cook at home.”", "bbox": [782.4, 61.3, 1055.2, 113.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Nandi says, “No! That’s a girl’s job. My mom does all the cooking at home.”", "bbox": [782.4, 136.7, 1064.3, 220.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Yes he can, Nandi. You can be anything you want to be,” says Teacher Langa.", "bbox": [782.4, 244.0, 942.0, 392.0], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "The class chants, “Yes you can!”", "bbox": [782.4, 449.9, 1056.0, 520.2], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 3, $$Milani says, “I want to build houses like my dad.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Milani says, “I want to build houses like my dad.”", "bbox": [56.7, 417.3, 503.2, 514.3], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 4, $$“No you can’t, that’s dangerous!” yells Phathu. “Yes she can, Phathu, as long as she loves it,” replies Teacher Langa. The class chants, “Yes she can!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“No you can’t, that’s dangerous!” yells Phathu.", "bbox": [793.7, 171.9, 1040.4, 255.9], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Yes she can, Phathu, as long as she loves it,” replies Teacher Langa.", "bbox": [793.7, 279.2, 1052.6, 363.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "The class chants, “Yes she can!”", "bbox": [793.7, 449.9, 1065.0, 520.2], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 5, $$Sthelo says, “I want to be a nurse.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Sthelo says, “I want to be a nurse.”", "bbox": [56.7, 53.1, 492.3, 119.7], "size": 28.5}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 6, $$The class bursts out laughing. “What is so funny?” asks Teacher Langa. Nandi replies, “Nurses are girls.” “There are male nurses too,” says Teacher Langa. “So class, can Sthelo be a nurse?” The class booms, “Yes he can!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The class bursts out laughing.", "bbox": [792.8, 61.3, 944.4, 113.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“What is so funny?” asks Teacher Langa.", "bbox": [792.8, 136.7, 937.4, 220.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Nandi replies, “Nurses are girls.”", "bbox": [792.8, 244.0, 1096.3, 264.1], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“There are male nurses too,” says Teacher Langa.", "bbox": [792.8, 287.3, 1060.7, 339.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“So class, can Sthelo be a nurse?”", "bbox": [792.8, 362.7, 1031.5, 414.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "The class booms, “Yes he can!”", "bbox": [792.8, 438.0, 1044.7, 508.4], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 7, $$“I want to be an artist and draw pretty pictures,’’ says Liyana.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I want to be an artist and draw pretty pictures,’’ says Liyana.", "bbox": [622.2, 54.7, 1047.4, 119.1], "size": 28.5}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 8, $$“That’s not a real job,” says Khutso and rolls his eyes. “That sounds lovely, Liyana!” replies teacher Langa. “Can Liyana be an artist?” “Yes she can!” shouts the class!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“That’s not a real job,” says Khutso and rolls his eyes.", "bbox": [793.7, 61.3, 922.5, 177.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“That sounds lovely, Liyana!” replies teacher Langa. “Can Liyana be an artist?”", "bbox": [793.7, 200.7, 1083.8, 284.6], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "“Yes she can!” shouts the class!", "bbox": [793.7, 447.6, 1065.0, 514.2], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 9, $$“I want to be an alarm clock,” says Phathu.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I want to be an alarm clock,” says Phathu.", "bbox": [34.9, 54.7, 511.5, 139.7], "size": 40.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 10, $$“Huh?” “What do you think, class?” asks Teacher Langa. The class booms, “ Yes you can! Yes you can!”$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "“Huh?” “What do you think, class?” asks Teacher Langa. The class booms, “ Yes you can! Yes you can!”", "bbox": [622.4, 63.2, 895.0, 361.1], "size": 36.6}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 11, $$Nandi when she hasn’t grows shared up. what she wants to be What do you think she could be?$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Nandi when she hasn’t grows shared up. what she wants to be", "bbox": [56.7, 61.3, 458.1, 113.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "What do you think she could be?", "bbox": [623.6, 66.0, 975.4, 106.0], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('yes-you-can', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 0, $$Hi! I’m a warrior and I’m fighting a monster, and I need you to help me. Yes, you! Come with me!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hi! I’m a warrior and I’m fighting a monster, and I need you to help me. Yes, you! Come with me!", "bbox": [87.9, 127.5, 397.1, 357.5], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 1, $$You see those ninja monkeys up there? I need you to shake this book so they fall out of the trees! Shake shake shake shake shake$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "You see those ninja monkeys up there? I need you to shake this book so they fall out of the trees! Shake shake", "bbox": [94.4, 60.1, 503.7, 319.1], "size": 27.8}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "shake shake", "bbox": [322.9, 347.1, 467.5, 380.8], "size": 25.5}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "shake", "bbox": [375.4, 415.1, 459.5, 454.2], "size": 31.9}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 2, $$Oh, no! Bats! I need you to blow them away! One, two, three – blo oo ooow!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Oh, no! Bats! I need you to blow them away! One, two, three – blo oo ooow!", "bbox": [103.7, 126.4, 468.4, 388.2], "size": 39.0}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 3, $$That got rid of them! This is the door to the monster’s cave. Knock to open it! knock! knock! knock!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "That got rid of them! This is the door to the monster’s cave.", "bbox": [134.4, 113.7, 432.5, 243.7], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Knock to open it!", "bbox": [123.6, 295.2, 443.3, 355.2], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "knock!", "bbox": [631.1, 39.3, 729.5, 91.9], "size": 33.7}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "knock!", "bbox": [806.8, 33.7, 902.7, 71.0], "size": 31.4}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "knock!", "bbox": [985.5, 36.1, 1082.8, 79.6], "size": 32.4}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 4, $$A spiky pit! Turn the book upside down so that I can walk across the roof! !niaga nwod kcab teg nac I os dnuora yaw thgir eht ti nrut woN .uoy knahT$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "A spiky pit!", "bbox": [362.6, 48.1, 490.4, 97.7], "size": 26.6}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Turn the book upside down so that I can walk across the roof!", "bbox": [266.5, 289.9, 486.9, 469.9], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "!niaga", "bbox": [641.9, 85.6, 725.8, 115.6], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "nwod", "bbox": [745.2, 149.3, 821.0, 179.3], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "kcab", "bbox": [892.4, 266.9, 960.0, 296.9], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "teg nac I os dnuora yaw thgir eht ti nrut woN .uoy knahT", "bbox": [682.3, 313.8, 1046.0, 443.8], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 5, $$Hyenas are chasing me! We need to go faster! Quick! Skip ahead two pages! Don’t look at the next page – just jump ahead!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hyenas are chasing me!", "bbox": [623.6, 61.9, 888.7, 85.9], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "We need to go faster! Quick!", "bbox": [623.6, 111.9, 938.0, 138.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Skip ahead two pages!", "bbox": [623.6, 164.0, 885.8, 188.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Don’t look at the next page –", "bbox": [623.6, 211.9, 942.5, 235.9], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "just jump ahead!", "bbox": [623.6, 261.9, 806.2, 285.9], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 6, $$Oh, no! I got eaten! Now you have to start the book again from the beginning!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Oh, no! I got eaten! Now you have to start the book again from the beginning!", "bbox": [654.8, 134.9, 976.8, 412.9], "size": 33.8}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 7, $$Phew! That was close! The hyenas almost got me! The monster is just past this yeti. Tickle the yeti to distract him, so I can sneak past! Tickle tickle tickle tickle!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Phew! That was close!", "bbox": [56.7, 115.0, 295.6, 139.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The hyenas almost got me!", "bbox": [56.7, 165.0, 356.3, 189.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The monster is just past this yeti.", "bbox": [56.7, 215.0, 415.5, 239.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Tickle the yeti to distract him,", "bbox": [56.7, 265.0, 381.9, 291.1], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "so I can sneak past!", "bbox": [56.7, 315.0, 273.7, 339.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Tickle tickle", "bbox": [93.2, 405.2, 228.6, 438.3], "size": 25.6}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "tickle tickle!", "bbox": [132.1, 483.5, 275.6, 517.7], "size": 25.4}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 8, $$It’s the monster! We’ve got to fight it! Show it we’re not scared! Say you’re a smelly monster! Say it out loud! Say it now!$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "It’s the monster! We’ve got to fight it! Show it we’re not scared! Say you’re a smelly monster! Say it out loud! Say it now!", "bbox": [87.9, 91.9, 458.7, 487.9], "size": 43.1}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 9, $$It didn’t work! I need you to make your scariest face to chase it away! Are you ready? One, two, three... Ya aa aa aa rgh!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "It didn’t work! I need you to", "bbox": [668.9, 133.4, 966.7, 157.4], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "make your scariest face to", "bbox": [670.3, 183.4, 965.3, 207.4], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "chase it away!", "bbox": [739.8, 233.4, 895.8, 257.4], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Are you ready?", "bbox": [733.6, 283.4, 902.0, 307.4], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "One, two, three... Ya aa aa aa rgh!", "bbox": [660.7, 333.4, 1006.1, 457.9], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 10, $$We did it! We scared it away! Highfive!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "We did it!", "bbox": [250.2, 308.1, 351.2, 332.1], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "We scared it away! Highfive!", "bbox": [196.5, 358.1, 404.9, 476.9], "size": 32.6}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 11, $$That was fun! Let’s go back to the start and do it all over again!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "That was fun! Let’s go back to the start and do it all over again!", "bbox": [73.7, 148.1, 457.2, 315.4], "size": 37.5}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 12, $$Almost at the back cover!$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Almost at the back cover!", "bbox": [45.8, 344.8, 180.9, 393.2], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('you-yes-you', 13, $$What are these pages for, anyway?$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "What are these pages for, anyway?", "bbox": [310.2, 236.6, 440.9, 311.4], "size": 22.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 0, $$This is Zandi. She has a friend that no one else can see. Some call him her imaginary friend, but Birdy Monster is very real to Zandi.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "This is Zandi.", "bbox": [794.3, 185.8, 906.5, 205.8], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She has a friend that no one else can see.", "bbox": [674.5, 245.8, 1026.3, 265.8], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Some call him her imaginary friend, but Birdy Monster is very real to Zandi.", "bbox": [684.9, 305.8, 1015.9, 355.8], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 1, $$Zandi and Birdy Monster play together everyday. Sometimes they mix up magic potions that will make you small or tall, or run very fast.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Zandi and Birdy Monster play together everyday.", "bbox": [305.5, 302.5, 501.7, 382.5], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Sometimes they mix up magic potions that will make you small or tall, or run very fast.", "bbox": [629.3, 104.0, 881.7, 184.1], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 2, $$Sometimes they are pirates... ...or superheroes.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Sometimes they are pirates...", "bbox": [161.7, 115.4, 405.3, 135.4], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "...or superheroes.", "bbox": [778.0, 424.2, 922.8, 444.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 3, $$Sometimes they climb trees to spy over the garden fence.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Sometimes they climb trees to spy over the garden fence.", "bbox": [725.9, 235.9, 977.7, 285.9], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 4, $$Sometimes they blow bubbles in the bath like hippos.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Sometimes they blow bubbles in the bath like hippos.", "bbox": [130.5, 260.0, 433.6, 310.0], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 5, $$Birdy Monster comes from the other side of the moon, where it is always night time.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Birdy Monster comes from the other side of the moon, where it is always night time.", "bbox": [652.1, 265.6, 1048.7, 315.6], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 6, $$When Zandi goes to bed, he glows in the dark so that she doesn’t get scared.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When Zandi goes to bed, he glows in the dark so that she doesn’t get scared.", "bbox": [142.2, 257.1, 407.7, 337.1], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('zandi-and-birdy-monster', 7, $$Birdy Monster has travelled everywhere, even to Port Elizabeth to visit Zandi’s Gogo Adeline.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Birdy Monster has travelled everywhere, even to Port Elizabeth to visit Zandi’s Gogo Adeline.", "bbox": [647.4, 438.6, 1053.4, 488.6], "size": 20.0}]$$),
